Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constra...ding_max_limit(25.10)  timing_constra...ding_max_limit(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_warn_for_timing_derate_exceeding_max_limit

Syntax
       timing_constraint_warn_for_timing_derate_exceeding_max_limit <double>

       Default: 100

       Value Range: 0 to 100

       Sets a limit on derate values. If a larger derate value is applied, the
       derates are still processed. However, the software issues a warning.

       Note:  It is recommended to specify derate values within the acceptable
       value range, because large derate values may cause errors  during  pro-
       cessing.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

